data.revised_prompt: Craft an artwork of a modern smart home security system equipped with luminous lights. The illustration should be of a minimalistic and uncluttered style, embodying simplicity and neatness. Emphasize on a central control panel displaying surveillance footage and a couple of exterior security cameras located around the house. Also integrate features such as an automated lock system at the main door, integrated alarm devices, and IoT enabled lights illuminating the home. Garner this in light soothing colors to accentuate the cleanliness and orderliness of the design.
